      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THUNDERLASH (2) is progressing well with another good run, placing by 8 lengths (25.87) in a Grade 6 at this track. Rates highly and will give a great sight. WE DIFFERENT (1) turned in a plain run last time when fifth at this track over 390m behind Fuseless Flynn (22.82) in a Grade 6. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from six starts. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. UTAH GUNN (5) was well back throughout but attacked the line to score by a neck (19.34) at Q Straight in Maiden. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Can measure up again. SHINE ON ANNIE (3) is not to be discarded.",
